## How to Use These Docs

- **Onboarding**: New team members should start with the [Project Management Overview](octoacme-project-management-overview.md)
- **Project Kickoff**: Review the [Project Initiation Guide](octoacme-project-initiation.md) for the first phase
- **Daily Operations**: Refer to [Execution & Tracking](octoacme-execution-and-tracking.md) for team rhythms and workflows
- **Release Planning**: Consult [Release & Deployment Guide](octoacme-release-and-deployment.md) before major releases
- **Continuous Improvement**: Use [Retrospective & Continuous Improvement](octoacme-retrospective-and-continuous-improvement.md) after milestones or incidents
- **Risk Management**: Reference [Risk Management & Communication](octoacme-risks-and-communication.md) throughout the project lifecycle

